summary:
Just an ECE (Enhanced Character Edit) Preset - enjoy!
:)
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=4]This is a simple ECE [/size][/b][b][size=4](Enhanced Character Edit) Slot Preset.

[/size][/b][color=#ffe599][size=5][b]Install[/b][/size][/color]: Simply drop in (Documents/my games/skyrim/CME_save)
[color=#ff0000][size=5]Make sure to rename the file to (_1_commonTriRaces) [/size][/color][color=#ff00ff][size=5]If you don't, then it won't show in the slot loader.

[/size][/color][color=#351c75][size=5][b]Requirements [/b][/size][/color][b][color=#000000][size=3](To make the character look as intended):

[/size][/color][/b]Any body mod, e.g: CBBE, UNP, SEVENBASE.
SG FEMALE TEXTURES: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?
;Make sure to download the file that associates with your body mod.
KS HAIRDOS (Optional, for hair): http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?
Eyes of Beauty (Optional, for eyes): http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
And finally, Enhanced Character Edit - obviously.

BaDamSH! :D That's it.

Share screenshots of your changes.
